CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1953, pg. 11 reads: "Beauties, All! - The above picture left out last week through misadventure, shows most of the lovely lovelies who took part in Cotton on Parade musicale fashion show given by the Links two weeks ago...Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Seven women, including woman in center wearing light colored skirt with flying birds and dark off the shoulder blouse, gathered on stage in A. Leo Weil school for Parade of Cotton fashion show
